    x86/bugs: Report AMD retbleed vulnerability
    
    Report that AMD x86 CPUs are vulnerable to the RETBleed (Arbitrary
    Speculative Code Execution with Return Instructions) attack.
    
      [peterz: add hygon]
      [kim: invert parity; fam15h]
    
